The paper discusses the performance analysis and design insights of millimeter wave integrated access and backhaul in 5G networks, which involves topics related to network infrastructure, wireless communication, and system design. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves information theory and signal processing, which are related to cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of millimeter wave technology in 5G networks, which is related to cs.AR (Augmented Reality and Virtual Reality) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
